---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";

const pageMeta = {
  title: "FAQ — Saving Harbor",
  description:
    "Frequently asked questions about coupons, verification, and how to report issues.",
};
---

<Base meta={pageMeta}>
  <Header />
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <article class="prose max-w-none lg:prose-lg text-on-surface">
      <h1 class="site-hero text-on-surface mb-6">FAQ</h1>

      <p>
        Below are answers to common questions about how SavingHarbor works, how
        we verify deals, and how you can stay updated.
      </p>

      <!-- FAQ list using native <details> for plain HTML/CSS accordion behavior -->
      <div class="space-y-4 mt-6">
        <details class="group bg-surface-2 rounded-2xl p-4" open>
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between text-base font-medium"
          >
            <span
              >What makes SavingHarbor different from other coupon sites?</span
            >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="none"
              aria-hidden
            >
              <path
                d="M6 8l4 4 4-4"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.75"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Our <strong>14 years of experience</strong> gives us insight—and credibility.
            We only share verified, high-value deals, and operate using technology
            designed for fast performance and user confidence.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-surface-2 rounded-2xl p-4">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between text-base font-medium"
          >
            <span>How often are offers updated?</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="none"
              aria-hidden
            >
              <path
                d="M6 8l4 4 4-4"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.75"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <short answer
              >Daily—our WhatsApp channel, Facebook groups, and email newsletter
              are our front lines. We monitor active offers and remove expired
              ones quickly.
            </short>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-surface-2 rounded-2xl p-4">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between text-base font-medium"
          >
            <span>Can I submit a deal?</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="none"
              aria-hidden
            >
              <path
                d="M6 8l4 4 4-4"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.75"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Absolutely — if you know of a great coupon or deal, send us the
            details via our
            <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-primary hover:underline"
              >Contact</a
            > page. We’ll review it for quality and include it if it qualifies.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-surface-2 rounded-2xl p-4">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between text-base font-medium"
          >
            <span>Do I need to pay to get offers?</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="none"
              aria-hidden
            >
              <path
                d="M6 8l4 4 4-4"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.75"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            No. All basic offers and deal alerts are free. Some premier or
            early-access offers may require subscribing to our newsletter or
            social channels—but never more than the value you get in real
            savings.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-surface-2 rounded-2xl p-4">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between text-base font-medium"
          >
            <span>How does privacy work at SavingHarbor?</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="none"
              aria-hidden
            >
              <path
                d="M6 8l4 4 4-4"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.75"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We keep your data safe. You control what information you share, and
            we never sell your personal data. See our <a
              href="/privacy-policy"
              class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a
            > for full details.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-surface-2 rounded-2xl p-4">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between text-base font-medium"
          >
            <span>How can I stay updated with the latest deals?</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="none"
              aria-hidden
            >
              <path
                d="M6 8l4 4 4-4"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.75"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Stay connected with us on our official channels for real-time
            updates and premier offers:
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1">
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61580887157989"
                  class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">Facebook</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://www.instagram.com/savingharbor/"
                  class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">Instagram</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://www.youtube.com/@SavingHarbor"
                  class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">YouTube</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://x.com/SavingHarbor"
                  class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">Twitter (X)</a
                >
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </article>
    <Footer />
  </main>
</Base>
